Winterbaume vendors a snapshot of the official AWS API Smithy models
under vendor/api-models-aws/ to drive its in-tree wire-type and
serialiser code generation. The upstream LICENSE and NOTICE files are
preserved alongside the vendored models. The upstream source is
available at https://github.com/aws/api-models-aws.
